Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:05.02,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\bord1.4\shad0\1c&HE6E6E6&\3c&H000000&}天空藍得嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:13.05,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\bord1.4\shad0\1c&HE6E6E6&\3c&H000000&}右手中的左手一直不知如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:20.55,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\bord1.4\shad0\1c&HE6E6E6&\3c&H000000&}於是像這樣整把整把的陽光拋在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:27.50,ED_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)\bord1.4\shad0\1c&HE6E6E6&\3c&H000000&}我們兩個人都還在這裡對吧
